MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2006-1697. Chillicothe Tel. Co. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 05-1298-TP-UNC. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

*1488It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
